    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E005",
      "type": "LEGAL_FINDING",
      "text": "I have no difficulty in concluding on the basis of all the evidence before me and consistent with the view of Dr Kirwilliam and Dr Wright that, with appropriate assistance, the Claimant could deal with issues and make decisions in this litigation.",
